name: WSC Real 09: World Championship Snooker - duplicate
summary: World Snooker where you can play against players from over 30 world billiards and snooker, standing among them: Higgins, Ronnie O'Sullivan, Ding Junhui and Graeme Dott. Can you be part of the powers of the Crucible and participating in 20 official tournaments like the World Snooker Championships and Masters, five championships and more.
